pageTitle: Duane Keffe D Davis accused in the of death of Tupac
keywords: Tupac,Tupac Shakur,duane keefe d davis,Keffe D,duane “keffe d” davis
description: Duane "Keffe D" Davis was indicted by a Nevada grand jury after being accused of planning the drive-by shooting death of Tupac Shakur in 1996. After decades of mystery.  A former gang leader, Duane has said the four shots that killed the rapper came from the vehicle he was riding in, a BMW driven by Death Row Records founder Marion “Suge” Knight in a convoy of about 10 cars.  When waiting at a light a white Cadillac carrying Tupac pulled up next to them and gunfire erupted, ending in the rappers death.
